This directory contains some useful tools.

The subdirectory traceviewerapp contains a graphical viewer for message
traces that can be captured as they traverse the stack. Trace capture
may be enabled by using the accessLogViaRMI flag so that the trace
may be retrieved by the trace viewer.

The subdirectory traceviewer contains a library that is used by
traceviewerapp.

The subdirectory responder contains a load-generator that is an xml based
template matcher and responder. This allows you to set up a script that
can respond to stack events on the basis of messages that match a template.
